@ "code-block" {
  "##": Code Block

  "body" = ```markdown
Notation as value:
```

  "eure-snippet" = ````eure
key = ```rust
fn main() {
    println!("Hello, world!");
}
```
````

  "body-2" = ```markdown
- Newline character is **not inserted at the head** of the code unless you manually insert a blank line.
- Newline character is **always inserted at the tail** of the last line of the code.
```

}

